------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                Pandoc-Goodies
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The following file:

    macros.pp

contain some PP macros taken from "The Pandoc-Goodies PP-Macros Library" and
readapted to our needs:

    https://github.com/tajmone/pandoc-goodies/tree/master/pp/macros

They are released under MIT License, with copyright notice:

Copyright (c) Tristano Ajmone 2017, MIT License.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                         GitHub Pandoc HTML5 Template
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The following files:

    GitHub.html5
    sass/_alerts.scss
    sass/_github-markdown.scss

where adapted from "GitHub Pandoc HTML5 Template", taken from "Pandoc-Goodies":

    https://github.com/tajmone/pandoc-goodies/tree/master/templates/html5/github

They are released under MIT License, with copyright notice:

Copyright (c) Tristano Ajmone, 2017 (github.com/tajmone/pandoc-goodies)
Copyright (c) Sindre Sorhus <sindresorhus@gmail.com> (sindresorhus.com)
Copyright (c) 2017 GitHub Inc.

"GitHub Pandoc HTML5 Template" is Copyright (c) Tristano Ajmone, 2017, released
under the MIT License (MIT); it contains readaptations of substantial portions
of the following third party softwares:

(1) "GitHub Markdown CSS", Copyright (c) Sindre Sorhus, MIT License (MIT).
(2) "Primer CSS", Copyright (c) 2016 GitHub Inc., MIT License (MIT).

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                Base16 Monokai
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The following file:

    sass/_base16-monokai.scss

uses the "Monokai" color scheme by Wimer Hazenberg:

    http://www.monokai.nl

The file was ported from YAML to SCSS by Tristano Ajmone, based on the source
file from Chris Kempson’s Base16 project:

    https://github.com/chriskempson/base16-builder/blob/master/schemes/monokai.yml

released under MIT License, with copyright notice:

Copyright (C) 2012 Chris Kempson

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                              Base16 London Tube
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The following file:

    sass/_highlight-ebnf.scss

uses some colors from the "Base16 London Tube" color scheme by Jan T. Sott:

    https://github.com/chriskempson/base16-builder/blob/master/schemes/tube.yml

whic is part of Chris Kempson’s Base16 project:

    https://github.com/chriskempson/base16-builder/blob/master/schemes/monokai.yml

released under MIT License, with copyright notice:

Copyright (C) 2012 Chris Kempson

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                         Highlight Syntax Definitions
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The following files:

    polygen.lang
    ebnf.lang

were created by Tristano Ajmone specifically for this project, but have then
become part of the official Highlight distribution (since v3.42).

Released into the public domain:

    Written by Tristano Ajmone:
        <tajmone@gmail.com>
        https://github.com/tajmone
    Released into the public domain according to the Unlicense terms:
        http://unlicense.org/

